{"tid":2207081,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"憎自己老豆老母既post見得多、有冇人係好愛自己個老豆老母覺得做佢地仔女好幸福。","createTime":"2020-09-18T02:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T00:17:50.000Z","uid":16063,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"259bf7c84d2e3d9aef82b20d542f160e218b01d0","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"非富貴家庭出身但覺得做到自己老豆老母個仔係呢世人最幸福既事。<br />\n全家黃。<br />\n阿爺果代已經係香港人從不返大陸。<br />\n由細到大都錫到自己痴線。<br />\n會發脾氣嘈交但永遠一兩日冇事。<br />\n真係好鍾意我老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f539f5b1af1b9524ed37dabda5039670771e45da","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"學業唔強逼 唔學壞唔食煙吸毒就夠<br />\n工作做自己鍾意既 唔好太大壓力就得<br />\n明明佢自己搵得果兩皮野都冇但都比哂屋企大部份洗費唔洗我比家用"},{"pid":"edbe4fb6094e3e6d0bed905a3ebb485d4eb3422c","tid":2207081,"uid":235527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f539f5b1af1b9524ed37dabda5039670771e45da","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"學業唔強逼 唔學壞唔食煙吸毒就夠<br />\n工作做自己鍾意既 唔好太大壓力就得<br />\n明明佢自己搵得果兩皮野都冇但都比哂屋企大部份洗費唔洗我比家用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"你好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7b74989dfb4d98028f030380d8a4c9d6185d61","tid":2207081,"uid":343544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"你就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年2月3月開始同老豆嘈左場大交 自從嗰日之後冇再理佢同佢講野 除左基本野"},{"pid":"80000f2a6568a16490c41376629afb42e4d4446c","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edbe4fb6094e3e6d0bed905a3ebb485d4eb3422c","tid":2207081,"uid":235527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f539f5b1af1b9524ed37dabda5039670771e45da","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:58:32.000Z","m