ec243","tid":2207081,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00d371a7d8c87381fe77725cddfd2a1a84d6a735","tid":2207081,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efcad2d3a72fe32f090d44a45f18cc3cbaa7fae5","tid":2207081,"uid":126947,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"多謝佢地做我父母<br />\n老豆好努力做嘢供曬我地幾隻讀U<br />\n媽媽一打幾照顧得我地好好<br />\n心靈上好滿足<br />\n佢地從來無係我地面前鬧過一次交<br />\n出街仲會拖到實<br />\n比咗充滿愛嘅家我地<br />\n全家黃 一齊鬧支那鬧政府<br />\n老豆仲會去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e87d66ff3918e4f66c2085de2794be1da43416","tid":2207081,"uid":202898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"926604a9b96b3a6bd6377e55d7fbbbf8a5cfc0f2","tid":2207081,"uid":57439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"其實全部都有兩面<br />\n<br />\n好: <br />\n兩老都黃<br />\n經濟無憂 (仲接濟埋我)<br />\n無病無痛<br />\n<br />\n壞: <br />\n對仔女要求好高, 壓力大到不行<br />\n細時一唔聽教就打, 打到皮開肉裂<br />\n而家純粹唔想俾親戚睇小所以先經濟支持我<br />\n乜話為我好就不停操控我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n物質條件真係唔錯, 但完全感受唔到愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"父母俾物質你先係最好既愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係男既既話 無物質再加對你冇要求<br />\n一個窮既廢柴女都溝唔到 又會俾人睇唔起<br />\n<br />\n女既話 你起碼唔洗因為物質出賣自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325eae0f610f9e958461cae6299000eaddaef538","tid":2207081,"uid":78613,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"以前好憎佢地....<br />\n我中五果時有強迫症同抑鬱 佢地完全唔明白我....<br />\n喺我沖涼同洗手果時關水制....<br />\n阿爸成日好唔衛生 阿媽成日係度煩全哂 我溫書果時講埋d癈話 我果時背書一比人嘈就會迫自己由頭背過<br />\n<br />\n到d同學個個出國讀書 我就成日話佢地癈搵唔到錢<br />\n<br />\n到而家我出黎做野再諗返 果時其實佢地都洗左好多錢喺我身上當然相對其中產果d唔算多 但都有比錢我補習有手機有電腦有錢買assignment book仲肯比我quit hd轉科<br />\n<br />\n到我而家垃圾學校grad 搵得雞碎咁多 都知道搵錢唔易<br />\n再諗返老豆真係日日都返工冇點放過假.....老母又係日日5點起煮早餐 番工 我仲要唔食佢d早餐 .... <br />\n<br />\n真係出到黎做野先知 一直最支持自己既真係自己父母..."},{"pid":"742c21d2ccd000c89aeb898a3401a03531e1f1a6","tid":2207081,"uid":176282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"其實如果唔知自己老豆老母之間啲衰野，會覺得自己屋企好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f393849a0b02e0e0c1560c93e9cdcbfe6d070e","tid":2207081,"uid":229353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efcad2d3a72fe32f090d44a45f18cc3cbaa7fae5","tid":2207081,"uid":126947,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"多謝佢地做我父母<br />\n老豆好努力做嘢供曬我地幾隻讀U<br />\n媽媽一打幾照顧得我地好好<br />\n心靈上好滿足<br />\n佢地從來無係我地面前鬧過一次交<br />\n出街仲會拖到實<br />\n比咗充滿愛嘅家我地<br />\n全家黃 一齊鬧支那鬧政府<br />\n老豆仲會去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以領養我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961b4c307eb56634ba18b229c65df63a8f007395","tid":2207081,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全家黃 <br />\n老豆老母錫到我燶<br />\n咩都以我為先 比錢供我讀書<br />\n成日同我講讀唔到唔緊要 唔好太辛苦自己<br />\n做人最緊要對得住天地<br />\n佢地想我讀理科 但我讀唔嚟而揀咗文科<br />\n佢地覺得冇問題 由我去追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係好有錢 但好多謝爸爸媽媽比咗咁大自由度我 咁愛我<br />\n無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa78451565349b9f52d6821a775d5e09e593f94","tid":2207081,"uid":229607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"媽煮野食世界級, 由all day breakfast 到印尼串燒飯到自制叉燒都係佢一手包辦, 識改衫縫紉又識玩獨木舟剷林行澗<br />\n<br />\n老豆有車有樓爭隻番狗, 佢講過一日佢未退休, 下至買米, 出街食飯, 上至屋企燈油火蠟架車油費佢都會一力承擔, 細佬去WH 果陣佢一唔夠錢就會泵水過去...<br />\n<br />\n相比起下, 我真係兩老每人既一半都學唔到...<br />\n<br />\n佢地兩個都有唔少缺點, 但作為父母已經係好PERFECT<br />\n<br />\n重點佢地上年8月後雖然都怕事無再遊行, 但都起碼係淺黃"},{"pid":"259ee9167058ab22babc937722c34cb6293d835c","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"961b4c307eb56634ba18b229c65df63a8f007395","tid":2207081,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全家黃 <br />\n老豆老母錫到我燶<br />\n咩都以我為先 比錢供我讀書<br />\n成日同我講讀唔到唔緊要 唔好太辛苦自己<br />\n做人最緊要對得住天地<br />\n佢地想我讀理科 但我讀唔嚟而揀咗文科<br />\n佢地覺得冇問題 由我去追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係好有錢 但好多謝爸爸媽媽比咗咁大自由度我 咁愛我<br />\n無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"我愛老母 我愛爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeb5929c016e4f99102e8ade11026b71b270734","tid":2207081,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259ee9167058ab22babc937722c34cb6293d835c","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"961b4c307eb56634ba18b229c65df63a8f007395","tid":2207081,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全家黃 <br />\n老豆老母錫到我燶<br />\n咩都以我為先 比錢供我讀書<br />\n成日同我講讀唔到唔緊要 唔好太辛苦自己<br />\n做人最緊要對得住天地<br />\n佢地想我讀理科 但我讀唔嚟而揀咗文科<br />\n佢地覺得冇問題 由我去追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係好有錢 但好多謝爸爸媽媽比咗咁大自由度我 咁愛我<br />\n無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"我愛老母 我愛爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"所以我連名都改埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3957d10b076d15dbc202deae4296f632be92ae72","tid":2207081,"uid":373762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:43:05.000Z","msg":"其實都係有好有唔好<br />\n <br />\n好：基因好，父母靚仔靚女，唔矮，唔甩頭髮<br />\n       <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壞：我完全遺傳唔到，我屌你老母"},{"pid":"e17e25681c131b93b7b28cfd364e5dfe803e9e46","tid":2207081,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"之前有一排會成日呻屋企人煩，又話好憎佢哋<br />\n但依家真係越嚟越愛佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先全家都係黃 我想做咩佢哋都支持<br />\n由細讀書都會set好高要求<br />\n但其實達唔到要求佢哋都唔會點 <br />\n仲會鼓勵我下次努力<br />\n之後以前會覺得佢管我太嚴，好煩<br />\n但依家諗返佢會咁都係我無交帶<br />\n啊爸由細都好錫我<br />\n有一排知我好窮又唔好意思開口借錢<br />\n成日偷偷地攝錢落我銀包<br />\n雖然我成日講嘢mean鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前同屋企人無乜交流<br />\n依家成日都會圍埋傾下計<br />\n傾多左，關係都好左勁多<br />\n不過我諗最重要都係立場一樣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17de0c7ee69feaadd88e52d35e29e57fa8b6daf2","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edeb5929c016e4f99102e8ade11026b71b270734","tid":2207081,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259ee9167058ab22babc937722c34cb6293d835c","tid":2207081,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"961b4c307eb56634ba18b229c65df63a8f007395","tid":2207081,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全家黃 <br />\n老豆老母錫到我燶<br />\n咩都以我為先 比錢供我讀書<br />\n成日同我講讀唔到唔緊要 唔好太辛苦自己<br />\n做人最緊要對得住天地<br />\n佢地想我讀理科 但我讀唔嚟而揀咗文科<br />\n佢地覺得冇問題 由我去追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係好有錢 但好多謝爸爸媽媽比咗咁大自由度我 咁愛我<br />\n無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"我愛老母 我愛爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"所以我連名都改埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"好爸爸係我最愛既馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf88000fa55b4f6fbd322c92ecfdf22d0b549d4","tid":2207081,"uid":246304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:17:50.000Z","msg":"比好多錢供我去外國讀書<br />\n每次返黎香港一落機就有好野食<br />\n而家出左去住<br />\n有時星期六日返去食飯<br />\n老豆老母都會煮好多好餸<br />\n最近我話想一齊住返<br />\n老豆即刻買左部最新型號唔平嘅電視放喺我房<br />\n因為佢知我由細到大都要聽住電視聲訓<br />\n雖然唔係大富大貴<br />\n但生活無憂<br />\n想要啲咩佢地都會滿足我<br />\n錫我錫到燶<br />\n唔止父母<br />\n所有媽咪啲兄弟姊妹同我阿婆阿公都好錫我<br />\n喺呢個家庭度成長真係好開心<br />\n其實我好愛佢地但因為怕醜所以冇講過出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}